text: David Jacobs (born 3 May 1989) is a South African cricketer. He made his first-class debut for Easterns in the 2013–14 CSA Provincial Three-Day Competition on 10 October 2013. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1989 births Category:Living people Category:South African cricketers Category:Easterns cricketers Category:North West cricketers Category:Place of birth missing (living people)
